# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ESFP Benchmark — .gitignore
# Keep: writeup, latest notebook, corpus, figures, scores, src
# Ignore: internal docs, old versions, raw data, third-party libs
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── OS / IDE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# ── Claude Code internals ─────────────────────────────────────
.claude/

# ── Internal strategy & competition docs (not ours to publish) ─
Kaggle AGI 赛事分析与策略.docx
Measuring Progress Toward AGI.docx
measuring-progress-toward-agi-a-cognitive-framework.pdf
Notion.pdf

# ── Internal deliverables (Word drafts, temp files) ───────────
delieverables/

# ── Literature survey (copyrighted PDFs) ──────────────────────
survey/

# ── Third-party reference notebooks & libs ────────────────────
kaggle-benchmarks/
kaggle-benchmarks-getting-started-notebook.ipynb
benchmark_demo/

# ── Old notebook versions (keep only v2.3) ────────────────────
ESFP_benchmark_v0.ipynb
ESFP_benchmark_v1.ipynb
ESFP_benchmark_v1.2.ipynb
ESFP_benchmark_v2.2.ipynb

# ── Old corpus version ────────────────────────────────────────
asset/ESFP_corpus.csv

# ── Old / intermediate results ────────────────────────────────
results/v1/
results/v1.2/
results/v2.1/
results/readable/

# ── Kaggle run metadata & raw cell outputs (not useful publicly)
results/v2.2/*.run.json
results/v2.2/*.task.json
results/v2.2/__results___files/
results/v2.2/__huggingface_repos__.json

# ── Raw parquet data (contains full model responses, ~4MB) ────
# Scores CSV and figures are kept; raw inference data is excluded
results/v2.2/ESFP_results/*.parquet

# ── Utility scripts (internal) ────────────────────────────────
utils/

# ── Python / env ──────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
*.egg-info/
